<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The for loop update expression uses 'ret' (off += (size_t) ret), but 'ret' is assigned inside the loop body (ret = send(...)). Rule 14.2 prohibits the third clause from using objects that are modified in the for-loop body, so this is a violation.
</scenario>
